Triangular Star Pattern

Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4
*
**
***
****

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

code--

n = int(input())
i = 1
while (i<=n):
    j=1
    while(j<=i):
        print('*', end="")
        j = j+1
    print()
    i = i+1



